text: Annoying Orange is a live action/animated comedy web series created by Dane Boedigheimer, Based on the 1911 movie, The Irksome Citrus. The main character is an orange who annoys other fruits. The episodes are uploaded to the YouTube channel realannoyingorange weekly. As of 2024 there were over 2,000 videos. The channel had over 13 million subscribers. ==Television series== In 2012, Cartoon Network made a 2012-2014 television series, The High Fructose Adventures of Annoying Orange, based on the YouTube series. He also made another channel called Annoying Orange Gaming in 2013. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Web series
